Text:
Classification: Scripted
Genre: Comedy
Status: New Series
Network: Adult Swim ( USA)
Airs: Thursdays at 11:55 pm
Runtime: 15 Minutes
Premiere: January 17, 2013

Newsreaders is a satire of the network television newsmagazine genre, from the creative team behind Adult Swim's highly successful comedy Childrens Hospital. Based upon the "Newsreaders" episodes of Childrens Hospital which aired during seasons two and three, Newsreaders will explore the vital issues that actually don't affect us every day, from hard-hitting investigations to harder-hitting heartwarming profiles.
